abstract: Shaun Donovan, a former cabinet secretary, files paperwork to run for mayor.
snippet: Shaun Donovan, a former cabinet secretary, files paperwork to run for mayor.
lead_paragraph: Shaun Donovan, a former housing secretary and budget director under President Barack Obama, filed paperwork on Monday to run for mayor of New York City.

abstract: A giant federal agency in turmoil faces more of it after a senior official is ousted.
snippet: A giant federal agency in turmoil faces more of it after a senior official is ousted.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — In a sign of continuing turmoil at the Department of Veterans Affairs, a deputy secretary in charge of key initiatives was dismissed on Monday, just as the agency rolls out complex changes to its health care system and a plan to address veterans suicide.

snippet: The two sides made their final speeches to senators with an eye toward the 2020 election.

abstract: The spread of the virus is likely to slow China’s progress in meeting the commitments it agreed to last month as part of the initial trade deal with the United States.
snippet: The spread of the virus is likely to slow China’s progress in meeting the commitments it agreed to last month as part of the initial trade deal with the United States.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The rapidly spreading coronavirus could claim one more victim: the United States-China trade deal.
